ime Olympians on this team have the potential to break out, but we are going with Smith as our choice.\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the eight first-time Olympians\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"this team\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2601}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2643}, {\"ngram\": \"our choice\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old forward won a national championship for the Stanford Cardinal in her college days, and she's only gotten better as a pro.\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2719, \"end\": 2736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.986836001405056e-18, \"text\": \"Stanford Cardinal\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 23-year-old forward\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2682}, {\"ngram\": \"a national championship\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"her college days\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"a pro\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She led the Portland Thorns to the NWSL league title in 2022, winning both the regular season MVP and Championship Game MVP.\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2832, \"end\": 2836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6544942058668796e-31, \"text\": \"NWSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\"}, {\"begin\": 2891, \"end\": 2894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_play